Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 客倌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出…出…出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山賊 殺人魔 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近來盡出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無…無面鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無面鬼  那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 那是我的木遁分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長 太假戲真做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 鳴人還真膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長的臉是最有害心臟健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼挖苦我嘛 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這濃霧中 也沒其他啥能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有大人像你這麼說鬼故事的 感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你膽小如鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不覺得那故事令人恐怖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就說個珍藏的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說每到這種時候就會出現那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:02:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了引導死者的靈魂 烏鴉作為先導出現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆柱上點亮的巨大鬼火就是證據 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃濃的大霧正是死者的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦相遇便會踏上前往死者國度的航程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是幽靈船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說就是這樣的濃霧 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 就是在這樣的濃霧中現身的幽靈船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的啦 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈船什麼的不過是古老的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 怎麼可能有那種東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我一點都沒信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可沒看出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有風吹動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈船…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 要去幽靈船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 世上沒有幽靈船什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是有嗎 就在那裡 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大和隊長說的如出一轍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是艘很可疑的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據航海法 不可以對漂流船隻置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊完成調查就能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就認命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此 不如陪著濃眉老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 要堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要夠堅強 管它是幽靈還是別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是先堅強點把暈船挺過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 青葉大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉可不是地板 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好忙 好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個忙碌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用它來開船的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這刷子真是歷史悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是船長的貴重物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你明明是個小孩 卻相當能幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人比一個人強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過比起兩人來 幹活可是人越多越快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不趕緊搞定你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不太會停下跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 我叫飛石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人是忍者嗎 很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標直指火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡最強大最偉大的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那船長比火影更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長不僅要強大要偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要處處溫柔地為夥伴著想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日 我也要成為一名船長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 等…等等先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影不僅強大 偉大 溫柔 為同伴著想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還相當有氣度 那個…之後還有…之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆都有各自的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 教教我那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是之前用刷子鏘鏘敲地的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是船長教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把刷子也是船長送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否也讓我們加入你們的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處搜查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是艘普通的船隻 大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是幽靈船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼幽靈船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是迷信來著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個不是人的靈魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帆柱上的火焰  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在船員之間被稱為幸運的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是發光的靜電氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜…靜電氣 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼帆柱上的烏鴉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般情況下 烏鴉可不會出現在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路休息的海鳥 被煙囪的煙給燻黑了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼幽靈船的話題就暫且告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們調查了一下這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上除你之外 沒有其他船員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的船員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種級別的船 需要相當的人數來運作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 刷子船長也沒在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們曾經都在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起海裡會有幽靈船這種愚蠢的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還潛藏著更恐怖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是傳說的海怪 牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不僅僅是只螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同一座小島般的巨型螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外殼堅硬無比 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被那巨大的鉗子抓到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼都會被碎屍萬段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且寄生於外殼之上的富士壺專吃活人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長和其他人 大家…大家被那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 忍者很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒那傢伙 替我給船長他們報仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 飛石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來打飛那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉大叔 帶飛石回船裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便替我轉告大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救大和隊長 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止牟黑大螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有將這件事轉告給同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事需要兩個人來做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉大叔更能冷靜地傳達消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得相當可靠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那個任務就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…你不害怕嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和那種怪物交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧 我的目標可是當上火影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了夥伴 一點都不害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了夥伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛石 你還小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有你一個得救也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕 船長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從登上這艘船起 這東西就一直伴隨我左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我保管好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了不少毛的刷子正是我的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能替我保管好 我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有未完成的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了信任我跟隨而來的同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守護這艘船到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是船長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我這就收拾掉你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是拯救了木葉村的英雄 漩渦鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去我們的船上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋 竟敢威脅我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是個怪物 你這傢伙才沒啥可怕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是怪物螃蟹 外殼太堅硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不僅堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還出人意料地敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉 我和船都搖晃不已 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊逃離這片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人正在為我們爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 請給我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法用我的拿手本領一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕緊解救出大和隊長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請借我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關上了 飛石做到了嗎 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然輕而易舉被抓 真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的外殼堅不可摧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說要瞄準柔軟的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木遁之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛石 把你的勇氣借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 怪物螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了飛石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你比我先實現願望了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間短暫 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經成為不輸火影的偉大船長了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時沒能跟大家一同作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在鳴人替我為大家報了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺舒坦了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抬舉我了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了飛石 才能打倒怪物螃蟹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你已經成為我們的同伴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過該告別了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛石 沒人會責怪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這強烈的責任感還真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不能成佛 所以我們都無法成佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 沒什麼好道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是被那混蛋螃蟹奪去了身軀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是相當舒坦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 藉著氣氛 大家來做例行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛石 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦之島
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來襲的暴風雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捲走的我們束手無策 出現在我們面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是可怕的鉤手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是何方神聖…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞著過去 人與人之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而現在深陷絕望之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了怒濤般的反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版火影忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火熱上映中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在電影院等著大家呢
